text: Vojtěch Mynář (4 May 1944 – 11 July 2018) was a Czech politician. From 2012 until 2014, he was a Member of the European Parliament, representing the Czech Republic. He was a member of the Social Democratic Party.Europarl – Vojtěch Mynář Mynář was born in Petřvald, Czechoslovakia. Mynář died on 11 July 2018 in Prague at the age of 74.Zemřel bývalý europoslanec Vojtěch Mynář ==References== Category:1944 births Category:2018 deaths Category:MEPs for the Czech Republic
